release.name: 2.0.0-rc1
release.body:
## What's Changed
* Fix wrong class reference in bootstrap section by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/261
* Feature/configuration improvements by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/262
* Add comments on Attributes for how to implement them by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/263
* Fix psalm inject inference by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/264
* Improve ContainerDefinitionBuilderContext names by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/265
* Fix inconsistent usage of VarExporter by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/266
* Update dependencies by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/267
* Update docs, prepare for 2.0.0-rc1 release by @cspray in https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/pull/268


**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/cspray/annotated-container/compare/v2.0.0-beta3...v2.0.0-rc1

issue.title: support psalm 5.x
issue.body:
As far as i can see there are no BC breaks affecting the plugin. 
So i don't think there is anything wrong with supporting psalm 5.x as well.
